387
00:22:02,985 --> 00:22:04,305
Since it has been decided,

388
00:22:04,385 --> 00:22:06,065
let's give it our best.

389
00:22:06,145 --> 00:22:07,825
We'll solve every problem along the way.

390
00:22:07,905 --> 00:22:08,745
Okay?

391
00:22:08,825 --> 00:22:11,425
If you ever need coordination,

392
00:22:11,505 --> 00:22:12,585
just let us know.

393
00:22:13,225 --> 00:22:16,665
Dawang and Xiaoduan will be in charge

394
00:22:16,745 --> 00:22:17,825
of this new project.

395
00:22:20,545 --> 00:22:21,465
Let's go.

396
00:22:26,385 --> 00:22:27,585
Let's go.

397
00:22:27,665 --> 00:22:28,745
Back to work.

398
00:22:28,825 --> 00:22:29,705
All the best.

399
00:23:05,425 --> 00:23:07,465
Hello, Jiaxu. I'm here.

400
00:23:07,545 --> 00:23:08,705
Where are you?

401
00:23:10,865 --> 00:23:12,305
Sorry, Sang Zhi.

402
00:23:12,385 --> 00:23:14,265
I don't think I can make it tonight.

403
00:23:19,505 --> 00:23:20,825
Are you working overtime?

404
00:23:21,785 --> 00:23:22,785
Yes.

405
00:23:22,865 --> 00:23:24,385
Order something for yourself.

406
00:23:24,465 --> 00:23:25,625
Don't starve.

407
00:23:28,025 --> 00:23:30,865
Your voice sounds off.

408
00:23:30,945 --> 00:23:33,785
Are you not feeling well?

409
00:23:34,785 --> 00:23:35,705
Not at all.

410
00:23:40,225 --> 00:23:41,305
What's wrong?

411
00:23:43,465 --> 00:23:44,945
It's just a little stomach pain.

412
00:23:45,585 --> 00:23:47,185
Maybe it's food poisoning.

413
00:23:47,265 --> 00:23:49,465
It's all right.
I'll just take some medicine.

414
00:23:49,545 --> 00:23:51,785
But shouldn't you go to the hospital?

415
00:23:53,345 --> 00:23:55,225
No need. This is nothing serious.

416
00:23:57,225 --> 00:23:58,625
