417
00:23:58,705 --> 00:24:00,345
Holding off the pain won't make it better.

418
00:24:01,425 --> 00:24:02,745
Where is your office located?

419
00:24:04,545 --> 00:24:05,905
Don't trouble yourself.

420
00:24:05,985 --> 00:24:06,865
I'm all right.

421
00:24:08,185 --> 00:24:09,785
Where is your office located?

422
00:24:12,945 --> 00:24:15,305
Gangbei Complex.

423
00:24:17,225 --> 00:24:18,665
Okay, I'll be right there.

424
00:24:21,545 --> 00:24:22,465
Hello, sir.

425
00:24:22,545 --> 00:24:23,385
Gangbei Complex.

426
00:24:36,905 --> 00:24:37,985
THE DREAM GAMES

427
00:24:43,545 --> 00:24:44,425
Sang Zhi.

428
00:24:46,185 --> 00:24:47,425
What are you doing here?

429
00:24:47,505 --> 00:24:48,985
-You came.
-Are you feeling better?

430
00:24:49,065 --> 00:24:50,905
It's nothing. It's just a stomachache.

431
00:24:50,985 --> 00:24:52,665
Wait here. I'll get a taxi.

432
00:24:52,745 --> 00:24:54,225
I'll take you to the hospital.

433
00:24:54,305 --> 00:24:55,185
Sang Zhi.

434
00:24:56,265 --> 00:24:58,505
-I'll go with you.
-Just wait here for me.

435
00:24:58,585 --> 00:24:59,625
It's all right.

436
00:25:00,665 --> 00:25:01,505
Let me take this.

437
00:25:03,905 --> 00:25:04,745
Lean on me.

438
00:25:05,625 --> 00:25:06,745
-I'm okay.
-Let's go.

439
00:25:07,665 --> 00:25:09,025
Come on. Watch your step.

440
00:25:12,305 --> 00:25:14,545
Are you helping an old man, kiddo?

441
00:25:14,625 --> 00:25:16,705
Can you walk on your own?

442
00:25:19,625 --> 00:25:20,465
I…

443
00:25:21,105 --> 00:25:22,985
-Slowly.
-I'm not saying you're a kid.

444
00:25:23,545 --> 00:25:24,545
It's all right.

445
00:25:27,585 --> 00:25:28,505
Be careful.

446
00:25:30,265 --> 00:25:31,585
Wait here for me.

447
00:25:31,665 --> 00:25:32,505
Okay.

448
00:25:32,585 --> 00:25:33,425
Wait here.

449
00:25:37,785 --> 00:25:38,705
Hey.

450
00:25:44,185 --> 00:25:45,025
Be careful.

451
00:25:45,745 --> 00:25:46,625
Be careful.

452
00:25:51,305 --> 00:25:52,905
I'll book a ride.

453
00:25:56,545 --> 00:25:57,385
What is the address?

454
00:26:21,905 --> 00:26:23,545
I didn't mean to do that.

455
00:26:23,625 --> 00:26:25,185
I didn't mean to either.

456
00:26:32,425 --> 00:26:34,225
Jiaxu, get in the car.

457
00:26:39,465 --> 00:26:44,865
HAIXIA TAXI

458
00:26:44,945 --> 00:26:45,825
Watch out.

459
00:26:45,905 --> 00:26:46,905
-I'm fine.
-Mind your head.

460
00:26:47,785 --> 00:26:48,625
Hello.

461
00:26:50,585 --> 00:26:52,065
-Hello.
-Hello.

462
00:26:54,265 --> 00:26:56,425
Is he drunk or something?

463
00:26:57,025 --> 00:26:59,065
-No.
-Is he going to throw up?

464
00:26:59,145 --> 00:27:00,545
No, sir.

465
00:27:00,625 --> 00:27:02,545
Sir, I won't throw up.

466
00:27:02,625 --> 00:27:03,505
I can hang in there.

467
00:27:03,585 --> 00:27:05,585
No, let me say this first.

468
00:27:05,665 --> 00:27:07,105
If you throw up in the car,

469
00:27:07,185 --> 00:27:08,145
you pay 200 yuan.

470
00:27:08,225 --> 00:27:09,145
Okay?

471
00:27:09,225 --> 00:27:10,505
He won't throw up.

472
00:27:10,585 --> 00:27:11,705
He has stomach pains.

473
00:27:11,785 --> 00:27:12,665
Go to the hospital.

474
00:27:12,745 --> 00:27:14,025
Take us to the hospital.

475
00:27:14,105 --> 00:27:15,985
-Okay.
-Sir, please hurry.

476
00:27:16,065 --> 00:27:16,905
Okay.

477
00:27:31,025 --> 00:27:31,985
OUTPATIENT BUILDING

478
00:27:32,065 --> 00:27:33,585
Judging by the ultrasound,

479
00:27:33,665 --> 00:27:34,665
