480
00:27:34,745 --> 00:27:36,865
And you waited to come in.

481
00:27:36,945 --> 00:27:38,825
Had you come any later,
it would've ruptured.

482
00:27:38,905 --> 00:27:40,185
What do we do now?

483
00:27:40,265 --> 00:27:41,465
One is conservative therapy.

484
00:27:41,545 --> 00:27:43,625
-We admit you and ease the inflammation.
-I see.

485
00:27:43,705 --> 00:27:44,585
The other method

486
00:27:44,665 --> 00:27:45,945
is going straight to surgery.

487
00:27:46,505 --> 00:27:48,145
-Then--
-Do the surgery.

488
00:27:48,225 --> 00:27:49,265
Okay.

489
00:27:51,785 --> 00:27:52,865
It will be all right.

490
00:28:01,865 --> 00:28:02,785
Sang Zhi.

491
00:28:04,945 --> 00:28:06,945
It's late. Head back to campus.

492
00:28:07,465 --> 00:28:09,225
It will be unsafe later.

493
00:28:09,305 --> 00:28:10,945
I'll wait for you outside.

494
00:28:12,825 --> 00:28:14,225
