501
00:28:49,585 --> 00:28:50,985
and never come to the hospital.

502
00:29:01,225 --> 00:29:03,025
"Avoid overworking.

503
00:29:04,345 --> 00:29:05,185
Avoid alcohol."

504
00:29:05,265 --> 00:29:06,145
MOM

505
00:29:11,385 --> 00:29:12,265
Hello, Mom.

506
00:29:12,905 --> 00:29:13,985
Hello, Zhizhi.

507
00:29:15,505 --> 00:29:17,865
It's past ten. Why haven't you called me?

508
00:29:18,625 --> 00:29:19,625
Are you at the dorm

509
00:29:19,705 --> 00:29:21,025
or hanging out with friends?

510
00:29:21,585 --> 00:29:22,505
No.

511
00:29:24,145 --> 00:29:27,425
Do you remember Sang Yan's classmate?

512
00:29:27,505 --> 00:29:29,825
He gave me physics lessons

513
00:29:29,905 --> 00:29:31,345
when I was in high school.

514
00:29:31,425 --> 00:29:32,305
Duan Jiaxu.

515
00:29:33,585 --> 00:29:35,305
I remember. Xiaoduan, right?

516
00:29:37,985 --> 00:29:40,185
We had plans to have dinner together,

517
00:29:40,265 --> 00:29:42,105
but he suddenly fell ill,

518
00:29:42,185 --> 00:29:44,025
so I took him to the hospital.

519
00:29:44,105 --> 00:29:45,145
Is he sick?

520
00:29:45,865 --> 00:29:46,745
What is it?

521
00:29:46,825 --> 00:29:47,865
Is it serious?

522
00:29:48,345 --> 00:29:49,865
Acute appendicitis.

523
00:29:49,945 --> 00:29:51,505
He's in surgery now.

524
00:29:55,265 --> 00:29:56,745
Poor thing.

525
00:29:56,825 --> 00:29:58,345
He doesn't have a family.

526
00:29:59,745 --> 00:30:01,825
What do you mean?

527
00:30:01,905 --> 00:30:03,745
His home is in Yihe, isn't it?

528
00:30:06,705 --> 00:30:09,105
I never told you about his background.

529
00:30:12,025 --> 00:30:12,905
Mr. Sang.

530
00:30:14,425 --> 00:30:15,745
There are 6,000 yuan left

531
00:30:15,825 --> 00:30:16,665
after the funeral.

532
00:30:16,745 --> 00:30:18,305
I'm returning this to you.

533
00:30:18,385 --> 00:30:20,265
I'll pay you the remaining balance

534
00:30:20,345 --> 00:30:21,385
