535
00:30:21,465 --> 00:30:24,105
Xiaoduan, keep the money for yourself.

536
00:30:24,185 --> 00:30:25,425
Don't rush to repay us.

537
00:30:25,505 --> 00:30:28,105
No, you have to take the money.

538
00:30:28,185 --> 00:30:29,025
Keep it.

539
00:30:30,785 --> 00:30:31,985
Keep the money and use it.

540
00:30:32,705 --> 00:30:33,825
You've been through a lot.

541
00:30:37,745 --> 00:30:38,865
I'm all right.

542
00:30:38,945 --> 00:30:40,305
It was nothing.

543
00:30:43,945 --> 00:30:44,905
Mr. and Mrs. Sang,

544
00:30:44,985 --> 00:30:47,545
