545
00:30:48,225 --> 00:30:50,305
There are other things I must attend to.

546
00:30:50,385 --> 00:30:51,385
I should get going.

547
00:30:52,305 --> 00:30:53,145
Thank you for your time.

548
00:30:54,985 --> 00:30:55,905
Xiaoduan.

549
00:30:56,785 --> 00:30:58,385
Dinner is ready.

550
00:30:58,465 --> 00:30:59,385
Eat before you go.

551
00:31:09,705 --> 00:31:11,145
No, thank you, Mrs. Sang.

552
00:31:11,225 --> 00:31:12,105
Thank you

553
00:31:13,065 --> 00:31:15,585
