555
00:31:19,105 --> 00:31:20,105
Thank you so much.

556
00:31:20,185 --> 00:31:21,465
You don't have to do this, child.

557
00:31:23,625 --> 00:31:24,505
Stand up.

558
00:31:26,265 --> 00:31:27,345
I'm going to go.

559
00:31:36,345 --> 00:31:37,905
The poor child.

560
00:31:37,985 --> 00:31:40,625
