562
00:31:43,545 --> 00:31:46,345
Sang Yan, look after him in school.

563
00:31:47,585 --> 00:31:48,425
Okay.

564
00:31:49,585 --> 00:31:51,145
In less than six months,

565
00:31:51,225 --> 00:31:52,705
he paid us back the rest of the sum.

566
00:31:54,265 --> 00:31:55,465
But his mom

567
00:31:56,945 --> 00:31:58,185
had passed away.

568
00:32:01,545 --> 00:32:02,425
Zhizhi.

569
00:32:03,625 --> 00:32:06,025
Don't stay out too late.

570
00:32:06,905 --> 00:32:08,345
Be safe on the way back.

571
00:32:12,465 --> 00:32:13,505
I'm hanging up now.

572
00:32:31,905 --> 00:32:33,505
He has to be hospitalized for seven days.

573
00:32:33,585 --> 00:32:35,545
He can't have solid food for now.

574
00:32:35,625 --> 00:32:37,585
He has to be on a liquid diet for a week.

575
00:32:37,665 --> 00:32:39,905
Should anything come up, just let us know.

576
00:32:41,305 --> 00:32:42,185
Thank you.

577
00:32:42,265 --> 00:32:43,145
Thank you.

578
00:32:55,625 --> 00:32:56,505
Jiaxu.

579
00:32:57,145 --> 00:32:58,425
I asked the nurses.

580
00:32:58,985 --> 00:33:00,305
They said these are what you need

581
00:33:00,385 --> 00:33:01,665
while you're in the hospital.

582
00:33:02,225 --> 00:33:04,105
But if you need anything else,

583
00:33:04,185 --> 00:33:05,345
let me know.

584
00:33:05,425 --> 00:33:06,945
I'll get it for you.

585
00:33:07,545 --> 00:33:08,745
Thank you, Sang Zhi.

586
00:33:09,785 --> 00:33:10,905
It's getting late.

587
00:33:10,985 --> 00:33:12,545
You should head back to campus.

588
00:33:14,585 --> 00:33:17,785
Get a taxi when you leave.

589
00:33:17,865 --> 00:33:19,905
Send the plate number to me.

590
00:33:20,665 --> 00:33:22,505
Let me know when you reach the dorm.

591
00:33:22,585 --> 00:33:23,425
Okay?

592
00:33:23,505 --> 00:33:24,465
Jiaxu.

593
00:33:25,705 --> 00:33:26,905
I'm not a kid anymore.

594
00:33:26,985 --> 00:33:27,905
Don't worry about me.

595
00:33:27,985 --> 00:33:29,225
I know what to do.

596
00:33:30,665 --> 00:33:31,585
Okay.

597
00:33:31,665 --> 00:33:32,625
Leave the things here.

598
00:33:32,705 --> 00:33:33,905
I'll put them away later.

599
00:33:39,505 --> 00:33:40,545
Did the wound hurt?

600
00:33:41,905 --> 00:33:43,105
I got anesthetics,

601
00:33:43,665 --> 00:33:44,905
so it doesn't hurt at all.

602
00:33:44,985 --> 00:33:45,865
I don't feel a thing.

603
00:33:46,385 --> 00:33:47,585
Don't worry.

604
00:33:47,665 --> 00:33:48,905
Go back now.

605
00:33:51,585 --> 00:33:53,105
I'll visit you tomorrow.

606
00:33:53,865 --> 00:33:55,705
Come when you don't have classes.

607
00:33:56,225 --> 00:33:57,865
I'm an adult.

608
00:33:57,945 --> 00:33:59,825
Don't trouble yourself for me.

609
00:34:00,505 --> 00:34:01,825
I'll be fine. Go on.

610
00:34:55,545 --> 00:34:56,945
Is she upset?

611
00:35:19,945 --> 00:35:22,545
She probably minds that.

612
00:35:38,705 --> 00:35:39,625
Hello?

613
00:35:41,705 --> 00:35:42,705
Hello, buddy.

614
00:35:43,545 --> 00:35:45,105
I heard you got your appendix cut out.

615
00:35:45,825 --> 00:35:46,745
How does that feel?

616
00:35:48,545 --> 00:35:50,785
Not bad. Would you like to try it?

617
00:35:52,345 --> 00:35:53,425
No, thank you.

618
00:35:53,505 --> 00:35:55,145
But I heard my sister took you there.

619
00:35:55,905 --> 00:35:56,785
Yes.

620
00:35:57,545 --> 00:35:59,545
Did you have to trouble her
for such a small problem?

621
00:35:59,625 --> 00:36:01,345
Couldn't you go to the hospital yourself?

622
00:36:01,425 --> 00:36:03,385
Did you call just to tell me that?

623
00:36:04,025 --> 00:36:06,625
No, I had dinner with my parents.

624
00:36:06,705 --> 00:36:08,145
They told me you were sick,

625
00:36:08,225 --> 00:36:09,545
so I called to celebrate.

626
00:36:10,265 --> 00:36:11,945
If there's nothing else, I'm hanging up.

627
00:36:12,025 --> 00:36:13,145
I'll carry on with my game.

628
00:36:15,185 --> 00:36:16,105
Hold on.

629
00:36:16,825 --> 00:36:18,505
I want to tell you something.

630
00:36:19,545 --> 00:36:20,905
What is it?

631
00:36:23,385 --> 00:36:25,025
Forget it. It's nothing important.

632
00:36:26,425 --> 00:36:28,025
Buddy, can you not do this every time?

633
00:36:28,105 --> 00:36:30,905
Just spill it like a real man!

634
00:36:31,505 --> 00:36:32,865
It's nothing. Bye.

635
00:36:34,345 --> 00:36:35,385
Hey!

636
00:36:50,265 --> 00:36:51,625
Why did you come back?

637
00:36:56,385 --> 00:36:57,305
Jiaxu.

638
00:36:58,185 --> 00:36:59,385
I gave it some thought.

639
00:37:01,265 --> 00:37:03,545
I should stay and look after you.

640
00:37:04,705 --> 00:37:07,385
If I were to fall sick
and had no one by my side,

641
00:37:08,145 --> 00:37:09,785
you would do the same for me.

642
00:37:10,745 --> 00:37:11,785
Right?

643
00:37:24,265 --> 00:37:25,425
Did you have dinner?

644
00:37:30,185 --> 00:37:31,065
I brought dinner.

645
00:37:40,905 --> 00:37:43,025
You haven't eaten.
Are you only having bread?

646
00:37:43,905 --> 00:37:44,905
Forget this.

647
00:37:44,985 --> 00:37:45,985
I'll order takeouts.

648
00:37:46,945 --> 00:37:48,505
Don't do that. I'm not hungry.

649
00:37:49,065 --> 00:37:50,585
You haven't eaten all day.

650
00:37:50,665 --> 00:37:51,945
You must be starving.

651
00:37:52,025 --> 00:37:53,025
I'm not hungry at all.

652
00:37:53,785 --> 00:37:55,945
If I were, I would get something to eat.

653
00:37:56,705 --> 00:37:57,825
I'm not a kid anymore.

654
00:37:58,465 --> 00:38:00,305
I don't need you to worry.

655
00:38:39,745 --> 00:38:41,545
She is stuffed like a pufferfish again.

656
00:38:58,865 --> 00:39:00,225
Jiaxu, what's so funny?

657
00:39:01,545 --> 00:39:02,825
Nothing.

658
00:39:11,225 --> 00:39:12,065
Where are you going?

659
00:39:12,905 --> 00:39:14,545
I'm going to freshen up.

660
00:39:15,625 --> 00:39:16,865
Go on.

661
00:39:49,865 --> 00:39:51,425
He can't get out of bed today.

662
00:39:52,265 --> 00:39:53,545
So he can't clean himself.

663
00:39:54,705 --> 00:39:56,105
Maybe I should help him wipe…

664
00:40:11,145 --> 00:40:12,385
Jiaxu.

665
00:40:12,465 --> 00:40:14,545
The doctor said you can't shower today.

666
00:40:14,625 --> 00:40:16,065
Do you want to wipe your face?

667
00:40:16,145 --> 00:40:17,105
Sure.

668
00:40:18,985 --> 00:40:19,905
I can help you.

669
00:40:20,505 --> 00:40:21,825
It's okay. I'll manage.

670
00:40:21,905 --> 00:40:23,905
What if you open up your wound?

671
00:40:25,705 --> 00:40:27,625
You'll have to spend even more days here.

672
00:40:30,545 --> 00:40:31,425
All right.

673
00:42:05,705 --> 00:42:07,865
I don't have a nice outfit
to wear to the movie!

674
00:42:08,505 --> 00:42:09,865
It's just across from campus.

675
00:42:09,945 --> 00:42:11,385
You still spent ages on your makeup.

676
00:42:11,465 --> 00:42:12,305
Let's go.

677
00:42:12,385 --> 00:42:13,905
Of course it's necessary!

678
00:42:13,985 --> 00:42:15,545
Girls want to look their best

679
00:42:15,625 --> 00:42:17,705
when meeting someone they like.

680
00:42:17,785 --> 00:42:19,105
You don't get it.

681
00:42:19,185 --> 00:42:20,425
Okay, I don't get it.

682
00:42:20,505 --> 00:42:22,265
Ning Wei is a love expert.

683
00:42:22,345 --> 00:42:23,505
Come on.

684
00:42:25,345 --> 00:42:26,625
Wait for me.

685
00:42:26,705 --> 00:42:28,545
You look good enough. Let's go.

686
00:42:28,625 --> 00:42:30,105
Just wait for a second!

687
00:42:30,185 --> 00:42:31,265
Hurry up.

688
00:42:31,345 --> 00:42:32,545
I know. Stop rushing me.

689
00:42:32,625 --> 00:42:33,585
Bye, Sangsang.

690
00:42:33,665 --> 00:42:34,505
Bye.

691
00:42:35,105 --> 00:42:36,025
Hurry up!

692
00:42:36,505 --> 00:42:37,345
I'll be right there.

693
00:42:37,425 --> 00:42:38,665
We're leaving. Bye!

694
00:42:38,745 --> 00:42:39,865
-Hurry up!
-See you later.

695
00:42:40,425 --> 00:42:41,705
Bye!

696
00:42:58,505 --> 00:42:59,625
It has been so long.

697
00:42:59,705 --> 00:43:01,345
You've learned how to put on makeup.

698
00:43:01,425 --> 00:43:02,865
You're indeed different from before.
